{"tid":583311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"練功券扮真$500流出市面　淘寶有售","createTime":"2018-03-07T01:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T06:27:49.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f1e92ec1fddd6566160082cd6fcbdf9ab3463692","tid":583311,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T01:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180307/photo/bkn-20180307070012059-0307_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180307082022\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180307%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180307070012059-0307_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180307082022&h=c29a1eb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180307/photo/bkn-20180307070012059-0307_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180307082022\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180307%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180307070012059-0307_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180307082022&h=9a84b791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「偽鈔」愈出愈逼真，連驗鈔機亦被「遮蔽」。近日在網上流傳，有商舖收到一張面值500港元的「練功券」，令人人心惶惶，擔心一不小心便墮入不法之徒圈套。不少網民紛紛留言，問「咩係練功券？」亦有人指出該券上印有「練功專用，禁止流通」的字樣，質疑為何「咁大隻字都見唔到。」<br />\n<br />\n有網民昨日（6日）在社交群組「Tai Po大埔」發文，提醒街坊要小心，聲稱收到朋友的訊息，指有人在觀塘樂華邨收到一張「練功券」。「如收一疊500蚊紙，逐張睇吓，免招損失！」圖中「練功券」逼真，清楚印上發鈔銀行、面值銀碼及鈔票編號等資訊。惟該券的右上方有兩行斜虛線，另亦在空白位置亦印有「練功券，票樣，練功專用，禁止流通」的字樣。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民隨即留言發問「咩係練功券？」有人無奈指「咁大隻字都見唔到。」更有網民提醒應立即報警，「收到要報警，因為可以告你藏有偽鈔。」有人在淘寶網找到不少「外幣練功券」的商品，其中100張不同面值的「港幣練功券」只售約10港元。根據網上資料，練功券全名為「銀行練功專用券」，是內地銀行職員用作練習點鈔的工具。<br />\n<br />\n如收到偽鈔，應立即交給警方或銀行處理，切勿試圖再次使用，否則有可能干犯香港法例第200章《刑事罪行條例》第99條的「行使偽製紙幣」罪行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說<br />\n<br />\nVera Lew：$10，$20，$50，淘寶都有，大家小心！<br />\n<br />\nPo Yip：仲有咩功，偷拐搶騙嗰種囉，國內人最有研究啦。<br />\n<br />\nNclbabii Ng：會計技能券&hellip;要仿真度咁高嘅嚟練嘅咩？<br />\n<br />\nBo Wong：要金精火眼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180307/bkn-20180307070012059-0307_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180307%2Fbkn-20180307070012059-0307_00822_001.html&d=ZFb6EgCh8lAR4UKiz3kEXcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=cf7481c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180307/bkn-20180307070012059-0307_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e5b0de69ed8f30da16a04cb2d69fe45cc96cb35f","tid":583311,"uid":39628,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T01:38:30.000Z","msg":"馬雲應該話哩d唔係假野"},{"pid":"d2cb391ec6bf394d89e0b2af009320860b57a1f0","tid":583311,"uid":5490,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T02:02:54.000Z","msg":"馬雲話假既比真野好"},{"pid":"5076207b237bbded1cbecfc9cedc59739d785fcf","tid":583311,"uid":5490,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T02:11:38.000Z","msg":"人人有功練"},{"pid":"9665cee8e89d353e6d6988578b88ee067861edef","tid":583311,"uid":58746,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5076207b237bbded1cbecfc9cedc59739d785fcf","tid":583311,"uid":5490,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T02:11:38.000Z","msg":"人人有功練"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T02:16:47.000Z","msg":"大佬呀, 人人有功練你都信, 唔呃你呃邊個呀?"},{"pid":"e63050ba0e8c1f738095338fd93e534cb53b9dfb","tid":583311,"uid":38041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9665cee8e89d353e6d6988578b88ee067861edef","tid":583311,"uid":58746,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5076207b237bbded1cbecfc9cedc59739d785fcf","tid":583311,"uid":5490,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T02:11:38.000Z","msg":"人人有功練"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T02:16:47.000Z","msg":"大佬呀, 人人有功練你都信, 唔呃你呃邊個呀?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T02:38:54.000Z","msg":"古拳法"},{"pid":"602732f6a1598b5a9c154e2980f4be085d0722f6","tid":583311,"uid":37431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9665cee8e89d353e6d6988578b88ee067861edef","tid":583311,"uid":58746,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5076207b237bbded1cbecfc9cedc59739d785fcf","tid":583311,"uid":